required to make 
sizeof(integer) == sizeof(real)
and
sizeof(logical) == sizeof(real)
(per f2c/readme)

--- f2c.h.orig	Tue Sep  7 13:46:24 1999
+++ f2c.h	Tue Dec  7 18:08:26 1999
